text: Jacques Valax (born August 23, 1951 in Albi, Tarn) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Tarn department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:People from Albi Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Jacques Valax
